{"id": "work_d065fdbb-1afd-5304-a006-e607589f1061", "title": "Remote research methods for Human\u2013AI\u2013Robot Teaming", "sources": [{"source": "dtic", "id": "pub.1140149980"}], "last_updated": "2026-03-09T19:37:22.880040", "abstract": "Abstract This study focuses on methodological adaptations and considerations for remote research on Human\u2013AI\u2013Robot Teaming (HART) amidst the COVID\u201019 pandemic. Themes and effective remote research methods were explored. Central issues in remote research were identified, such as challenges in attending to participants&#x27; experiences, coordinating experimenter teams remotely, and protecting privacy and confidentiality. Instances of experimental design overcoming these challenges were identified in methods for recruitment and onboarding, training, team task scenarios, and measurement. Three case studies are presented in which interactive in\u2010person testbeds for HART were rapidly redesigned to function remotely. Although COVID\u201019 may have temporarily constrained experimental design, future HART studies may adopt remote research methods to expand the research toolkit.", "publication_date": "2021-08-03", "doi": "10.1002/hfm.20929", "url": "https://dtic.dimensions.ai/details/publication/pub.1140149980?and_facet_researcher=ur.01033404537.13", "citation_count": 0, "authors": [{"author_id": "author_a826bca4-dda2-5829-9237-38b25486e77f", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_b39d74ac-b75e-5bae-a7cf-b38ed1c6a03e", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_172fb24d-5615-50b8-a317-514123c7fd69", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_69047214-183a-50b7-a87c-309e6851cf8d", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_c4a7cd8b-d12c-504c-89f8-9967817837a4", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_abb007cc-9c91-5e53-9971-551b868ed96a", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_2e634162-3ca1-5dbe-8d06-dea85cf82a67", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_72ecbe0e-be6b-5f5f-bdc6-875ab77678fc", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_8c337707-e543-56e3-8a0d-6f8a484d5279"}, {"author_id": "author_8e004942-6f0d-5387-a764-97a0a7144af0", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}, {"author_id": "author_6dbdd9c3-c4ec-50c7-a6cf-53b423fc338c", "org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87"}], "orgs": [{"org_id": "org_6ed4c9c7-c192-50ea-90e2-e37b1ca71f87", "role": "affiliation"}], "topics": [{"topic_id": "topic_8c2772de-7365-54bb-86a3-75f20fd0d80c", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_5f6206c5-8f78-54c7-a345-ae82f68b33a5", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_1237268d-b86c-5069-9aac-593eb92b7d86", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_af68473e-a2da-5c43-b5c9-914ed8f8a528", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_1f527ace-8971-52b8-a08e-e947afeab94e", "score": 1.0}, {"topic_id": "topic_43df9421-5b7a-5756-bbeb-8020d41dd6d0", "score": 1.0}], "created_at": "2026-03-09T19:37:22.880040"}